'''Janis''' is the mother of a baby born with an imperforate anus who was operated on by [[Oliver Lebackes]], [[Arizona Robbins]], and [[Alex Karev]].

==History==
After her son's surgery, Dr. Lebackes gave her the good news that it had been a total success and her son would live a healthy life.
